            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "when you create an app with:\n\n```\napp = Flask(__name__)\n```\n\nyou can add a static_path parameter:\n\n```\napp = Flask(__name__, '/stylesheets')\n```\n\nand you're done.\n\nRegarding the templates I have to dig into jinja2 'Environment' which is created together with the app but you can give a look to this:\n\nhttps://github.com/mitsuhiko/flask/issues/221\n\nwhich suggests you should subclass Flask and customize your jinja2 environment.\n"
